Title: The Face of Our Enemies
Description:
Powerful foes lurk among the enemies Fyrakk summoned into the Emerald Dream.

I have not seen Cassaphine since she came up out of the barrows. 

Find her, and assist our allies by striking down these leaders.
ObjectivesText: Defeat Fyrakk's powerful lieutenants and secure the battlefield.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Meet Merithra in the Fields of Reverie.
